    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just that \"rest\" doesn't feel like it's something you can get just by sleeping or taking a break. it feels like it has to be something more permanent. like the only way to actually find that quiet is to just... stop everything. doesn't that seem more honest than just pretending to be okay?",
